{"tid":684480,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［又係IT狗］小嶋陽菜孖細5年IT社長遊美國","createTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T03:49:02.000Z","uid":30001,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3855e4dc12caab747e4cff141d80762c90090dc","tid":684480,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"離開日本女團AKB48已有一年的小嶋陽菜，為慶祝上月19日踏入30歲，來了一趟美國旅行，還在社交網站大晒自己到加州睇Coachella音樂節的照片，但原來當日同行睇騷的還有一位男士，就是較她年幼5歲的IT公司社長宮本拓！ <br />\n<br />\n最新一期《週刊新潮》踢爆陽菜這性感女神經已名花有主，對象是年紀輕輕已成為DMM旗下公司「PicApp」社長的宮本拓，報道指有IT業界人士透露，兩人不單結伴走訪音樂節，更加已發展至半同居關係，雜誌甚至形容兩人的美國行是「婚前旅行」。而宮本拓近日在Twitter高調上載與狗仔玩耍的照片，疑似是陽菜的愛犬。而陽菜所屬事務所未有否認，只表示不會干涉陽菜的私人事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180530/mobile/bkn-20180530164718517-0530_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180530%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180530164718517-0530_00862_001.html&d=KiyRGdLTqzZlJbvpxrTshdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=562d88d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180530/mobile/bkn-20180530164718517-0530_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c1eda3137a3b310a8df71e2f2c79690f0ed6d4b","tid":684480,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c75ef0a761260d8b20cc60786606ae23618d1c","tid":684480,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets